      "side": 1,
      "message": "it\u0027s not clear to me that this covers timeout of a step. e.g. if the recipe runs a test which may take a maximum of 3 minutes and so times out, is this resource exhaustion?\n\nAdditionally, in this case, is this required to be an INFRA_FAILURE status? What if the recipe is documented to enforce \"this test may only take X time; longer counts as FAILURE\"?",
